			<div class="content" id="post-content-4777385">
									

<p>Going to have to echo those above me - this is a villain monologue through and through, and I half expected some sort of Syndrome aside to pop up: &quot;ah you caught me monologuing!&quot;. The most boring way to convey information is to flat out tell us, and that's really all this is.</p>
