			<div class="content" id="post-content-4777771">
									

<p>Generally agree that the monologue seems over the top, and I'm not entirely sure about the Scarlet King and the Church of the Broken God working together. It just doesn't sit right with me. The whole &quot;All the Bad Guys Team Up&quot; proposal as a whole seems rather melodramatic, and with all the differing characterizations we've seen of the different GOIs over the years, I'd be rather disappointed if they all do just toss aside all their differences to become just united, straightforward enemies against the Foundation that need to be stopped again. Hoping we see more nuance in how the GOIs react, and maybe some that might like the current status quo.</p>
<p>However, I'm still hype as hell to see a reexamination of the Foundation's roots and ties to Bowe. No vote for now.</p>

