<p>While I understand the concerns of others who have downvoted, I have to say this was definitely my cup of tea. As someone who’s not familiar with past Resurrection canon, this story still felt understandable and that was important to me. While the monologue aspect of this is a point of contention, I think it makes perfect sense to an organization like the Chaos Insurgency where almost everyone is kept in the dark and would need a large-scale announcement to set the facts straight to everyone involved.</p>
